<span class="label">10.</span><cite>CPT® (Current Procedural Terminology) | AMA [Internet]. [cited2021 May 10]. Available from: <a href="https://www.ama-assn.org/amaone/cpt-current-procedural-terminology" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.ama-assn.org/amaone/cpt-current-procedural-terminology</a></cite>
